# Dashboard System Architecture

## Core Components Structure

The dashboard system is built around these main components in [src/components/dashboard/](mdc:src/components/dashboard/):

- [DashboardLayout](mdc:src/components/dashboard/dashboard-layout.tsx) - Main layout wrapper with SidebarProvider
- [DashboardSidebar](mdc:src/components/dashboard/dashboard-sidebar.tsx) - Collapsible sidebar using shadcn/ui Sidebar
- [DashboardHeader](mdc:src/components/dashboard/dashboard-header.tsx) - Header with breadcrumbs
- [DashboardBreadcrumb](mdc:src/components/dashboard/dashboard-breadcrumb.tsx) - Smart breadcrumb with ellipsis for >5 items
- [Navigation config](mdc:src/components/dashboard/navigation.ts) - Centralized navigation structure
- [Types](mdc:src/components/dashboard/types.ts) - TypeScript interfaces

## Key Architecture Principles

1. **Use shadcn/ui Sidebar Components**: Always use the official Sidebar components instead of custom implementations
2. **Collapsible by Default**: Sidebar should always use `collapsible="icon"` for icon-only collapse mode
3. **Smart Breadcrumbs**: Automatically truncate breadcrumbs >5 items with ellipsis dropdown
4. **Centralized Navigation**: Use `defaultSidebarNavigation` or create structured navigation configs
5. **TypeScript First**: All components must be fully typed with provided interfaces

## Usage Patterns

### Standard Page Layout

```tsx
import {
  DashboardLayout,
  defaultSidebarNavigation,
  type BreadcrumbItem,
} from '@/components/dashboard';

const breadcrumbItems: BreadcrumbItem[] = [
  { title: 'Dashboard', href: '/dashboard' },
  { title: 'Current Page' },
];

export default function MyPage() {
  return (
    <DashboardLayout sidebarNavigation={defaultSidebarNavigation} breadcrumbItems={breadcrumbItems}>
      <div className="space-y-6">
        <div className="space-y-1">
          <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Page Title</h1>
          <p className="text-muted-foreground">Page description</p>
        </div>
        {/* Page content */}
      </div>
    </DashboardLayout>
  );
}
```

### Navigation Structure

Navigation items must include:

- `title`: Display name
- `href`: Navigation URL
- `icon`: LucideIcon component (required for collapsed mode)
- `badge`: Optional badge (string | number)
- `disabled`: Optional disable state
